# ğŸ•µï¸â€â™‚ï¸ BlackBox Logger

![PyPI](https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/blackbox-logger)
![License](https://img.shields.io/github/license/avi9r/blackbox_logger)


A universal request/response logger for **Django**, **Flask**, **FastAPI**, and other Python apps.  
Automatically logs requests and responses, user info, IP address, and more â€” with **masked sensitive data** â€” into a log file and SQLite database.

---

## ğŸš€ Features

- âœ… Logs all HTTP requests and responses  
- âœ… Logs to both `blackbox.log` file and SQLite DB (`blackbox_logs.db`)  
- âœ… Automatically masks sensitive fields (e.g., `password`, `token`, etc.)  
- âœ… Logs user (if available), IP address, and user agent  
- âœ… Skips HTML content in logs to avoid noise  
- âœ… Works out-of-the-box in **Django**  
- âš™ï¸ Easy integration in **Flask** and **FastAPI**

---

